<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>响应式设计示例</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>响应式网页设计</h1>
        <nav>
            <button class="menu-toggle">菜单</button>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="#media-queries">媒体查询</a></li>
                <li><a href="#flexbox">Flexbox布局</a></li>
                <li><a href="#grid">Grid布局</a></li>
                <li><a href="#images">响应式图片</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="media-queries">
            <h2>媒体查询</h2>
            <p>媒体查询允许根据设备特性应用不同的样式：</p>
            <pre>@media (max-width: 768px) {
  body {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .nav-menu {
    display: none;
  }
}</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="flexbox">
            <h2>Flexbox布局</h2>
            <div class="flex-container">
                <div class="flex-item">项目1</div>
                <div class="flex-item">项目2</div>
                <div class="flex-item">项目3</div>
            </div>
            <pre>.flex-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.flex-item {
  flex: 1;
  margin: 10px;
  padding: 20px;
  background: #e0e0e0;
}</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="grid">
            <h2>Grid布局</h2>
            <div class="grid-container">
                <div class="grid-item">网格项目1</div>
                <div class="grid-item">网格项目2</div>
                <div class="grid-item">网格项目3</div>
                <div class="grid-item">网格项目4</div>
            </div>
            <pre>.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="images">
            <h2>响应式图片</h2>
            <p>使用srcset和sizes属性提供不同分辨率的图片：</p>
            <img src="small.jpg"
                 srcset="small.jpg 480w, medium.jpg 800w, large.jpg 1200w"
                 sizes="(max-width: 600px) 480px, (max-width: 1000px) 800px, 1200px"
                 alt="响应式图片示例">
            <pre>&lt;img src="small.jpg"
     srcset="small.jpg 480w, medium.jpg 800w, large.jpg 1200w"
     sizes="(max-width: 600px) 480px, (max-width: 1000px) 800px, 1200px"
     alt="响应式图片"&gt;</pre>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>响应式设计让网站在各种设备上都能良好显示</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>